The paper proposes a novel algorithm for object detection, which is a subfield of computer vision (cs.CV). The algorithm involves clustering and weighting, which are common techniques in machine learning (cs.AI) and statistical modeling (cs.LG). The paper also evaluates the algorithm using various object detectors, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR) subcategories.
